年 38 了，也希望自己 40 岁以前能跑个半马玩玩。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-36fb06da18ce1a65a8fcb69ccb3728c6_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "33 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/494609447"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iiobt7+Cst+1OEAMaCDcyMTk0MDU3IKSY3osGMAE4pAFAK3IJNDk0NjA5NDQ3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "44_1636225548.6474752", "card_id": "Q_268869162", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 163}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "中国哪些城市的羊肉最好吃？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-13aeb0a7930224f5d3eba8ac489881e4_1440w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "33 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/268869162"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iiobt7+Cst+1OEAMaCDIxOTgxNDQ4IOirqtUFMAM4lARALHIJMjY4ODY5MTYyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1636225548.647917", "card_id": "Q_496787857", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 101}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待 42.8% 的未成年人因玩手机向家长索要过身份证，如今防沉迷成效如何？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "11 月 5 日，据伽马数据发布的《中国游戏产业未成年人保护进展报告》显示，85.8% 未成年用户在游戏中受防沉迷系统限制，这说明近九成孩子在玩游戏因防沉迷受阻，如何评价当下防沉迷的成效？报告中还显示未成年人防沉迷挑战中，42.8% 未成年人直接向家长索要过身份信息，家长还能为了孩子健康生活做些什么？ 此前，8 月 30 日，国家新闻出版署下发《关于进一步严格管理 切实防止未成年人沉迷网络游戏的通知》，针对未成年人过度使用甚至沉迷网络游戏问题，进一步严格管理措施，坚决防止未成年人沉迷网络游戏，切实保护未成年人身心健康。封面新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-07487e63bcc0ec013fc886ab0c0b509e_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "32 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/496787857"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8Iiobt7+Cst+1OEAMaCDcyNjc4NTYwIIv8kowGMAw4kwJALXIJNDk2Nzg3ODU3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": 